{"tid":2508780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自我身體檢查！了解自己的便便[多圖]","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T04:29:24.000Z","uid":5655,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6d226e303aa851b9930eb9468ab7c1e52900cd16","tid":2508780,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfLfrOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfLfrOf.jpg&h=29b70df5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M494j8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM494j8f.jpg&h=30a6df8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDp72mB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDp72mB.jpg&h=5140e642&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W7w2ReX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7w2ReX.jpg&h=6070deb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gotwKzX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgotwKzX.png&h=9df136d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWf7hUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWf7hUY.jpg&h=7391e7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8Q3AGD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8Q3AGD.jpg&h=eec0e93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每天上完廁所，你有習慣回過頭去觀察你的「便便」嗎？無論是大便的形狀、顏色、氣味，甚至是排便的次數，都會忠實反應出身體的健康狀況，正常的大便應該是土黃色或偏綠（吃很多蔬菜的人）的「香蕉型」，不軟不硬、成形而且沒有味道，如果你的大便如此，代表你的飲食生活、精神狀態非常好請繼續保持，反之則要特別注意，及早改正不良生活、飲食習慣，防止疾病「腸」來報到。<br />\n<br />\n我們一天吃三餐，標準的排便次數應該「一天三次~三天一次」，如果以小時計算，腸胃道正常轉移時間的範圍約18~48小時，若一個人攝取到來自水果、蔬菜、全穀類的膳食纖維建議攝取量，則糞便會較多且較柔軟，也較容易通過腸道，但若缺乏膳食纖維、水、活動力不足等，就會有便秘的問題。"},{"pid":"f107d09df4d5376af3c55951fbfb428013f90f63","tid":2508780,"uid":306439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n食緊咖哩飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.g